{"tid":404941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家最想自己活到幾歲？","createTime":"2017-09-18T13:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T13:27:20.000Z","uid":54581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3702debaa83c443bd86eccd8314ab246c2485eff","tid":404941,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"我唔大貪<br />\n<br />\n60歲過世已經好滿足<br />\n<br />\n頭廿年青春期 老豆老母養 無憂無慮<br />\n<br />\n中間25~30年 盡下仔女責任 出黎搵錢養家養父母<br />\n再拍下拖結下婚咁 仔女就唔生了<br />\n<br />\n最後10年就慢慢退下火線 過下日晨咁 <br />\n<br />\n反正60歲打後都係病痛多，又無後生咁有活力，前邊講左唔生仔直頭無牽無掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6373bc081ffb7e99f865b7d9ec5bc27f24f6cf23","tid":404941,"uid":145881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"40夠喇"},{"pid":"ed7f632c630cd1084847a5f4a0e7350beff3a7b6","tid":404941,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16a8a825b1c3f92f9f581dad98f8fb388e55738","tid":404941,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"永生"},{"pid":"3ed51f01a75d284b5d375d6029e6a99361da8301","tid":404941,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"２０"},{"pid":"45de1f3751a434892c31f733554ae6a0ce0e1b20","tid":404941,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"一係永遠既年輕<br />\n<br />\n唔係就50夠啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我要既係短暫既輝煌"},{"pid":"58402364f68e0948d41e50884c8142fa2ae674ac","tid":404941,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"頭腦清醒冇病冇痛行得走得嘅話活到100歲都得,如果妹下妹下老人痴呆症就死撚咗佢算喇"},{"pid":"2b4dced5d2fd7541ceab17d8d51e713e5602beff","tid":404941,"uid":136924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"80<br />\n我好想有多